sesedit a securities class action lawsuit involving the company was filed in july  under samet v lionbridge technologies inc et al in the united states district court for the southern district of new york in  a lionbridge employee was awarded noneconomic damages of usd  and economic damages of usd  due to failure by the company to fulfil its obligation to help the employee obtain a green card a  court case involved an unfair dismissal claim by a former lionbridge employee fired for union recruitment activities at the companys warsaw office to protect employment conditions protests in support were held in denmark spain poland and ireland awards and recognitionedit every year since  lionbridge has been named a top  training outsourcing company   chosen by microsoft as vendor of the year for providing microsoft with development test and globalization services worldwide   named in the global  a list of the worlds best outsourcing firms by the international association of outsourcing professionals   lionbridges geofluent received  product of the year award from customer interaction solutions magazine   finalist in the third annual marketo revenue performance excellence awards   named one of americas  most trustworthy companies by forbes   listed as the worlds number one language services provider by common sense advisory   received customer magazine product of the year award referencesedit  lionbridge tops list of worlds  largest language service providers for fourth consecutive year prnewswire   lionbridge expands geofluent realtime translation for omnichannel customer care smart customer service   company overview galaglobalorg   our company  lionbridge technologies lionbridgecom retrieved    taus members tausnet   bert esselink  the evolution of localization pdf guide to localization multilingual computing and technology   lionbridge completes acquisition of bowne global solutions prnewswire   lionbridge acquires costa ricas darwin zone nearshoreamericascom   lionbrid